S. mails, 360 passengers and one million treasure, (received from Pacific Mail steamship Golden Gate, which left San Francisco Aug. 18, and arrived at Panama Aug. 31 at 4 A. M ,) and arrived at this Port at 9 A. M., 10th inst., without having a single case of sickness on board.
